content: The best icon pack on the store and I've bought hundreds of them. There is something special about this icon pack, something this developer does with his packs and its something i cant go without now that I'm used to it. Namely that the icons are much more detailed. They have a higher pixel quality than other icon packs. And there is so much here to work with They look great at all (common phone resolution) sizes. You can tell the difference immediately. And there are seriously like several thousands of icons. If there is an icon missing for one of ur apps, don't u worry because there are so many that you can easily find one that is close enough to what you need, or at least a good enough replacement. You have your icons of actual apps and games that are creative and vivid and pleasing to the eye. You have all your system icons. But then there are just like so many more icons that are of things or simikar enough but many are random. There is so much here. Its like digging through a used icon store with both excellent and good icons aplenty. Then thete are also some above average ones. But its all like new. Overall this pack is like my go-to one honestly. I see the dev has many more packs and they scare me cuz if they have the depth that this one does... i havent even fully explored this one yet. There is still a lot of meat on the bones of this pack for me. Get it. Buy it as your default pack. Its awesome. Dev, thank you for supporting this. You have my favorite icon pack on the store, hands down.
